<td style="border-right: 1px solid #AAA; text-align: center; width: 25%;"><span style="font-size:80%;">Dr.Stevens</span></td>
<td style="text-align: center; width: 25%;"><span style="font-size:80%;">机动特遣队Mu-13（“Ghostbusters”-捉鬼敢死队）</span></td>
